CM_ "Renault 5 E-Tech (CMF-BEV). CHECKSUM uses CRC-8 poly 0x1D init 0 with
per-message XOR. Most messages use a 7-byte protected body before the checksum
byte; 0x134 LKA_CMD is the exception with a tail-positioned CHECKSUM (byte 16,
XOR 0xEB) protecting bytes[17:24].";


